# Personal, version-controlled skills are whitelisted below. Everything else in
# this directory lives on disk but stays untracked: ECC marketplace skills,
# continuous-learning's generated `learned/`, and any other installer-managed
# skills. They are reproducible (re-install via their installers) and machine-
# local, so they do not belong in the dotfiles history.
#
# To sync a new personal skill: add a `!/<skill-dir>/` line below.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/co-review/
!/codex-plan-review/
!/codex-spec-review/
!/brief/
!/lib/
!/post-merge/
!/reconcile/
!/ship/
!/todos/
!/weekly/
!/wrap/
